SRFCNN

fully convolutional neural network for single image superresolution

- due to an unresolved memory leak in tensorflow.js or other, this works only in chrome(dirty workaround)
- your browser has to support webgl and your gpu has to have a minimum of 2gb memory
- this is an alpha version, just to show what's possible.
- made by (@BenjaminWegener) using Image Super-Resolution Using Deep Convolutional Networks and Striving for Simplicity: The All Convolutional Net
